It's truly love at first bite for her! 😍  She can't resist the smell of real meat from Chewy Cubes Beef and Lamb. She’s also having fun with its crunchy texture filled with a tasty filling of Crunchy Pockets Milk and Chicken, it truly is the love of her life. 

You can grab it for your dogs to bring a burst of happiness. Pedigree Tasty Bites is now available at pet shops, supermarkets, and online stores.
